PHRASE.LANG: TARDIS stands for “Time And Relative Dimension In Space.” The TARDIS looks like a 1950’s wooden Police Phone Box on the outside, but is of infinite proportions on the inside. Amaze your friends when they discover the wonder of Time Lord technology. Doctor Who logo © 2013 and TM BBC. Licensed by BBC WW Ltd. [#Legal]

TARDIS est synonyme de "Time And Relative Dimension In Space." Le TARDIS ressemble à une Police Box 1950, Téléphone en bois à l'extérieur, mais prend des proportions infinies à l'intérieur. Surprenez vos amis quand ils découvrent les merveilles de la technologie Time Lord. Doctor Who logo © 2013 and TM BBC. Licensed by BBC WW Ltd. [#Legal]
